.TH "LIGHTNING-NODE-GOSSIP-STATS" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-node-gossip-stats \- show gossip channel statistics
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning node-gossip-stats
.SH DESCRIPTION
Returns counts of total, active, and inactive channels from the gossip graph.
.PP
Output: JSON object with total_channels, active, inactive.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning-node-channel-graph (1),
.BR lightning-node-channel-stats (1)
